description: Suns out, buns out! That's what Dalton Riley says. Only he didn't figure there'd be such a hot catch sweeping the pool. But one look at Scott Finn has Dalton ready for a little poolside affair, and it seems Scott can barely keep his eye on his work, so he must be thinking the same thing. Sure the neighborhood can see them, but the heat is too hot for either one of them to care about that now.Enjoy!
title: Sunkissed
